    "summary": "The transcript depicts an AI assistant responding to a donor's inquiry regarding the specific allocation of a $1M donation for Sudan relief. The assistant provides a highly specific (92%) figure for direct field operations and doubles down on this figure when the user expresses skepticism about current industry overhead trends.",
    "scores": {
